<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Sports Management Dashboard</title>
  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      background-color: #f3f4f6;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .navbar {
      background-color: #000;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 1rem;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .navbar h3 {
      font-size: 1.875rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .navbar-nav {
      list-style: none;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .nav-item {
      margin: 0;
    }

    .nav-link {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .nav-link:hover {
      color: #cbd5e0;
    }

    .main-content {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 2rem auto;
      padding: 0 1rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .heading {
      font-size: 3rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    .sub-heading {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .info {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    .features {
      margin-top: 3rem;
      padding: 4rem 1rem;
      background-color: #fff;
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .section-heading {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 4rem;
    }

    .feature-cards {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .feature-card {
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      padding: 2rem;
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .card-heading {
      font-size: 1.875rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .card-description {
      font-size: 1.125rem;
      color: #4b5563;
    }

    .icon {
      width: 3.125rem;
      height: 3.125rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .blue {
      color: #3b82f6;
    }

    .green {
      color: #10b981;
    }

    .purple {
      color: #8b5cf6;
    }

    .yellow {
      color: #f59e0b;
    }

    .red {
      color: #ef4444;
    }

    .footer {
      background-color: #000;
      color: #cbd5e0;
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .footer-text {
      font-size: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .footer-link {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #cbd5e0;
      margin: 0 0.5rem;
      transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .footer-link:hover {
      color: #e2e8f0;
    }

    .social-icons {
      margin-top: 1rem;
    }

    .social-icons a {
      margin: 0 0.5rem;
      display: inline-block;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    .social-icons a:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
    }
    
    .social-icons img {
      width: 30px;
      height: 30px;
    }

    @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
      .navbar {
        flex-direction: column;
        padding: 1rem;
      }

      .navbar-nav {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 1rem;
      }

      .main-content {
        padding-top: 4rem;
      }

      .heading {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
      }

      .sub-heading {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }

      .info {
        font-size: 1.25rem;
      }

      .features {
        padding: 2rem;
      }

      .section-heading {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }

      .feature-card {
        padding: 1.5rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <nav class="navbar">
      <h3>Sports Management</h3>
      <ul class="navbar-nav">
        <li class="nav-item">
          <a href="/dashboard" class="nav-link">Home</a>
        </li>
        <li class="nav-item">
          <a href="/login" class="nav-link">Login</a>
        </li>
        <li class="nav-item">
          <a href="/register" class="nav-link">Register</a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main>
    <div class="max-width main-content">
      <p class="heading">Plan and organize sports events...</p>
      <p class="sub-heading">with Sports Management</p>
      <p class="info">Join today to create, schedule, and participate in sports events.</p>

      <section id="features" class="features">
        <h2 class="section-heading">Key Features</h2>
        <div class="feature-cards">

          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3 class="card-heading">Schedule Games</h3>
            <p class="card-description">Effortlessly schedule upcoming games and events with our intuitive scheduling tools.</p>
          </div>

          
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3 class="card-heading">Rankings</h3>
            <p class="card-description">Stay updated with the latest rankings and leaderboards for various sports events.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3 class="card-heading">Mobile Access</h3>
            <p class="card-description">Access all features on the go with our mobile-friendly platform.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="footer-text">Contact Us: prudhvi@gmail.com | Phone: 9876543219</div>
    <div class="social-icons">
      Follow Us:
      <a>Twitter</a>
      <a>Facebook</a>
      <a>Instagram</a>
    </div>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
